nipulating spectral changes to focus on target-dominant segments, I developed algorithms that significantly enhance speech intelligibility in challenging auditory environments.\n\nOverall, my work bridges the gap between advanced AI techniques and practical applications, striving to create robots that can understand and interact with the world in a more human-like manner.)']But you do not have to communcate with other agents.
